(41, 13, 34, 46, 15, 58, 58, 'his work', 'Work and Vigilance in Service', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of being diligent in one''s work. Mark 13:34 speaks of giving authority to servants for their tasks, while 1 Corinthians 15:58 encourages steadfastness in the work of the Lord, assuring that their labor is not in vain.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
