(41, 13, 36, 20, 6, 9, 11, 'find you sleeping', 'Awakening from Spiritual Slumber', 'This connection highlights the theme of vigilance versus slumber. Both passages emphasize the consequences of being spiritually or physically asleep, warning that neglect can lead to dire outcomes.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
