(41, 14, 1, 2, 12, 6, 20, 'feast of the passover', 'Passover and Death Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the significance of the Passover in relation to death and deliverance. In Mark, the timing of Jesus'' impending death coincides with the Passover feast, which commemorates the Israelites'' deliverance from death in Egypt.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
