(41, 14, 1, 43, 13, 1, 1, 'feast of the passover', 'Connection of Passover Themes', 'Both passages emphasize the significance of the Passover, with Mark highlighting the impending event and the plot against Jesus, while John focuses on Jesus'' awareness of his impending departure during the same feast. This connection highlights the thematic continuity of the Passover in relation to Jesus'' mission.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 14, 1, 5, 16, 1, 8, 'feast of the passover', 'Passover and Death Connection', 'This connection highlights the significance of the Passover in both passages, with Mark referencing the imminent Passover feast while the Deuteronomy passage outlines its observance. Both passages emphasize the importance of sacrifice and remembrance associated with the Passover.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
